rows.label: tlk45370151_03_msg0001
rows.name:
That fool Roderich! He just had to
act carelessly, and look where it
got us! Taken advantage of by Iira!

rows.label: tlk45370151_03_msg0002
rows.name:
If it weren't for Acedia's
intervention, who knows
what might have happened!

rows.label: tlk45370151_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I suppose we'd better
be thankful for that.

rows.label: tlk45370151_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I expect the pro-war faction of
the Senate will be forced to lie
low for a while after this, too.

rows.label: tlk45370151_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Roderich's actions were reckless
and terrible, but in the end, they
may have worked to our advantage.

rows.label: tlk45370151_03_msg0006
rows.name:
I'm sure Roderich himself
will not escape a harsh
sentence, of course...
